            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-dc29ddeed3d8eddc-f09fcd twpub-dc29ddeed3d8eddc-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK JIN'GANG WISDOM ***</p></div>"
