            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-dc29ddeed3d8eddc-f09fcd twpub-dc29ddeed3d8eddc-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
